<plot>Skip Heitzig traces the footsteps of Paul the Apostle from Israel on the road to Rome. Joining Skip are biblical consultants Dr. Steven Collins and Steve Jahss. You'll hear and see the importance of each historical site from Paul's missionary voyages. From Jerusalem through Turkey to Greece and, finally, to Rome itself, this documentary makes Paul's extraordinary journey come alive.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?587370</url></doc>
